text:
My purpose is to make an impact,
whether that's in 1:1 dialogue

or in the case
discussions, in meetings

that I have, and
really everything
that I do in the future.

I'm super excited about
leveraging my newfound access

and resources to improve
the lives of others.

I come from very
humble beginnings

and folks from my
community just wouldn't

be able to do that in
the same way that I am.

So I'm super excited about
bringing my perspectives

and my background
to all of my work

and my personal
relationships as well.

I hope to make an impact one
day as a wife and a mother

on my family, as a positive
influence in my community,

as well as in our nation
in the broader world
